TI  - Propofol suppresses migration and vascular mimicry of breast cancer MCF-7 cells by down regulating interleukin-6
AU  - Shi-Yi Tian
AU  - Ming-Qing Peng
AU  - Min Li
JO  - Pakistan Journal of Pharmaceutical Sciences
VL  - 38
